data.description: Don't miss your opportunity on this rare 5 bedroom, 3 bath Acacia Cove dream home with 3 car garage, RV gate and your very own heated swimming pool! Close to all the desired amenities the Arrowhead Ranch area has to offer: great dining, shopping and recreation. Sellers are willing to contribute up to a total of $12,000.00 towards buyers' closing costs and/or interest rate buydown so call now to book your private tour of this beauty BEFORE it's sold!
